{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"许下愿望之后，我破坏了疑似医院的设施@虽然想本想继续破坏掉剧团@但因为是在昏迷状态下被转移到这里的@我已经完全不知道那个剧团的位置了","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-1"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20281.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"翻过树木茂密的山@我发现自己正在日本的一座小岛上","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-2"},{"narration":"我在附近的村落里见到了普通的日本人@虽然对他们说了医院的事@但周围的人都只是困惑","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-3"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20311.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"在那之后，我本想至少对警察报告一声@所以坐上了来回小岛和本州的定期联络船@却直接被送去进行矫正教育@在忙于处理各种事情的期间@又被转移到了新的设施","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-4"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_50071.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":104102,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm23_puella04","chara":[{"id":104102,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-5"}],"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"也是太没现实感了","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104102,"motion":300,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-6"}],"enableSkipAutoTurn":1,"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"难道是梦吗…？@怎么可能…"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104102}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":104102,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-7","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-1-6"}],"enableSkipAutoTurn":0,"nameCenter":"莉薇娅","textCenter":"（虽然最开始抓住